67
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,960
What do you mean by holding leverage?

68
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,400
Cheol Woong.

69
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:22,490
I know that you hate Team Captain Oh,

70
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:24,500
but he sincerely apologized to you.

71
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:27,730
Also, our family needs him.

72
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:29,940
We need him?

73
00:03:29,940 --> 00:03:32,380
You should forgive him now.

74
00:03:32,380 --> 00:03:35,390
I mean, I suppose you would need him, Mom.

75
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:38,570
He played a major role in helping you acquire your wealth, Mother, is he not?

76
00:03:38,570 --> 00:03:41,930
Cheol Woong, I did that for your future–

77
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:44,160
No, no, no.

78
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:48,230
It wasn't for my future,

79
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:51,750
but you nearly screwed up my future.

80
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:54,080
Your real estate...

81
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:57,050
was purchased with the knowledge of the development plans ahead of time.

82
00:03:57,050 --> 00:03:58,710
It's not just me.

83
00:03:58,710 --> 00:04:00,600
Everyone does it!

84
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:02,440
You know that much!

85
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,110
Everyone does it?

86
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:08,220
Ordinary people don't have access to such power or information.

87
00:04:08,220 --> 00:04:11,320
And there's no way Oh Man Ok did that for you, purely out of loyalty.

88
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:14,440
And you are not the type who wouldn't compensate him for it, either, Mom.

89
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,610
That will all become evidence later.

90
00:04:16,610 --> 00:04:18,080
That is necessary.

91
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,590
