92
00:04:19,590 --> 00:04:21,770
It also needs to be given carrots for it run!

93
00:04:21,770 --> 00:04:23,470
That's...

94
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:26,550
because a horse is a beast that can be tamed.

95
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:31,000
Oh Man Ok is not a beast you can tame, Mom.

96
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,990
Cheol Woong.

97
00:04:32,990 --> 00:04:35,930
We have your father.

98
00:04:35,930 --> 00:04:40,820
Team Captain Oh can't do whatever he wants against us or betray us.

99
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:45,450
Everything that Oh Man Ok knows about us,

100
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:50,060
that will all be a deadly weapon that he can use against us, Mom!

101
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,630
Cheol Woong.

102
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,650
Why are you being like this?

103
00:04:53,650 --> 00:04:58,520
Your father, you, and I all agreed to move past this already.

104
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:01,160
Let's stop this now, please?

105
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:06,130
Oh Man Ok threatened me before.

106
00:05:06,130 --> 00:05:07,700
In this spot.

107
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,950
What?

108
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,250
He threatened me,

109
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:15,600
knowing that I murdered someone and had Doo Hak hyung take the blame.

110
00:05:20,530 --> 00:05:21,630
And...

111
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,590
And what else did he threaten you with?

112
00:05:25,890 --> 00:05:29,380
<i>Also, the fact that the person closest to you</i>

113
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:32,880
<i>had the definitive witness killed.</i>

114
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:38,410
I'm asking just in case,

115
00:05:39,410 --> 00:05:41,200
but Joong Ho ahjussi...

116
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,400
were you responsible?

117
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:49,090
What are you talking about?

118
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:52,620
Are you trying to say that I ordered him to kill Ahjussi?

119
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:57,530
That was an accident!

120
00:05:57,530 --> 00:06:01,370
If you weren't responsible, then tell me so.

121
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:05,630
Don't look at me with those eyes!

122
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,950
It's not me.

123
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,540
I'm not responsible for that!

124
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:11,690
Then...

125
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:13,200
was it Father?

126
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,700
Cheol Woong.

127
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:17,550
Tell me the truth, Mom.

128
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:23,250
Do you know what that guy said to me?

129
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:27,400
He said the one closest to me did it.

130
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:31,160
So, please tell me the truth.

131
00:06:32,290 --> 00:06:34,810
Lee Joong Ho threatened your mother.

132
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:36,590
Honey...

133
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:41,370
- Excuse me? 
 - While Team Captain Oh was acting as your mother's security,

134
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:44,240
he found out about Lee Joong Ho's threats.

135
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,360
I found out later after receiving his report

136
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,750
that he took care of it by himself.

137
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:52,590
Does that make any sense?

138
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:54,350
How could Team Captain Oh do that by himself?

139
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:57,460
There are times in our field when we take action first and then report later.

140
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,470
You know that as well.

141
00:06:58,470 --> 00:06:59,750
But even so, that is a bit–

142
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:01,890
Don't make this a problem any more.

143
00:07:01,890 --> 00:07:05,050
You can't make this a problem, and you shouldn't do so, either.

144
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:10,060
You want me to tell you the truth?

145
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,440
The truth is...

146
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:16,250
knowing the truth is not always right and worthwhile.

147
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:19,130
An uncomfortable truth can actually cause chaos to society,

148
00:07:19,130 --> 00:07:21,150
and destroy a nation.

149
00:07:21,150 --> 00:07:23,350
At times, it is more often than not

150
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:26,050
more right and worthwhile not to know it or to cover it up.

151
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:29,990
But if you still feel that you must know the truth, then go ahead and try it.

152
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:31,930
In return,

153
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:34,480
you will have to lay everything down.

154
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,130
Your ambitions,

155
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,970
and your love.

156
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:07,130
I was so shocked as well.

157
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:11,530
I didn't know Team Captain Oh would go to that extent.

158
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:15,910
Did Ahjussi...

159
00:08:17,010 --> 00:08:19,470
really demand money from you?

160
00:08:20,470 --> 00:08:22,190
Yeah.

161
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:25,700
And so did you give it to him?

162
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:29,640
That real estate agency Doo Hak's mother is running

163
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:34,050
got started using my money.

164
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:36,930
It's the truth.

165
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,700
Honestly,

166
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,180
I can't believe it.

167
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,990
He's not someone who would do that.

168
00:08:59,990 --> 00:09:02,230
I was the same.

169
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:07,680
I guess it was hard for him to come up here without any money.

170
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,500
He was like...

171
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:14,930
a real father to me.

172
00:09:14,930 --> 00:09:16,670
I know.

173
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:20,870
So, that's why

174
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:24,160
I couldn't really tell you these things.

175
00:09:56,610 --> 00:09:59,160
<i>When I look at you, Cheol Woong,</i>

176
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:02,870
<i>you take after your grandfather.</i>

177
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:07,260
<i>You will become a great person</i>

178
00:10:07,260 --> 00:10:10,130
<i>just like your grandfather.</i>

179
00:10:10,130 --> 00:10:14,120
<i>Well, If I could be like him in the slightest, I would be happy.</i>

180
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:17,130
<i>Aigoo, how you're also humble...</i>

181
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:20,750
<i>You are truly an adult. Really.</i>

182
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:22,300
<i>Cheol Woong...</i>

183
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:25,740
<i>let me give you a hug.</i>

184
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,520
