195
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:23,600
<i>Listen carefully to what I'm about to say.</i>

196
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:26,960
<i>There's a slush fund ledger I gave to the NSA.</i>

197
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,190
<i>If that's revealed to the world...</i>

198
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:31,280
That...

199
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,020
You still have it, right?

200
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,550
Yeah, I remember it.

201
00:11:34,550 --> 00:11:35,690
Why do you ask about that?

202
00:11:35,690 --> 00:11:38,540
You said not to open it or show it to anyone.

203
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:41,230
Because it's so dangerous and you would get hurt.

204
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:43,090
I wouldn't be around,

205
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:45,890
so you wouldn't have anyone to protect you.

206
00:11:46,890 --> 00:11:49,810
Within the slush fund ledger,

207
00:11:49,810 --> 00:11:52,120
there is a notebook.

208
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,380
[Present] 
 Yeah.

209
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:55,500
I can say it.

210
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:58,220
I can say it's not true.

211
00:11:58,220 --> 00:12:01,120
Even if I die and meet those two,

212
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:04,170
I can say it's not true!

213
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:12,650
Even if such ridiculous things took place,

214
00:12:12,650 --> 00:12:15,810
would Doo Hak hyung have lived not saying anything?

215
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:18,200
What kind of crazy bastard

216
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:21,160
would live such a long sentence in prison for someone else, Jung Shin?

217
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:24,490
- Isn't that right?
- That's right.

218
00:12:24,490 --> 00:12:27,290
Lee Doo Hak sure happens to be a crazy bastard.

219
00:12:27,290 --> 00:12:28,960
Choi Cheol Woong.

220
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,980
You were such a good friend to me.

221
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:34,150
And a friend I felt bad for.

222
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:38,280
I really hoped it wasn't you.

223
00:13:44,070 --> 00:13:45,920
<i>That day,</i>

224
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:49,350
<i>it was raining heavily.</i>

225
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:52,560
<i>My father returned from Cheol Woong's house completely soaked and...</i>

226
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,340
Doo Hak...

227
00:13:55,180 --> 00:13:59,120
<i>looked down at me while I was crouching under the eaves.</i>

228
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:03,630
<i>With such a pitiful look in his eyes.</i>

229
00:14:04,530 --> 00:14:06,030
<i>And...</i>

230
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:09,710
<i>with a gaze that said he had no choice,</i>

231
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:16,400
<i>that I should go to jail instead of Cheol Woong,</i>

232
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:22,010
<i>and that I shouldn't forgive him.</i>

233
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:28,850
<i>Jung Shin was looking down at me in disbelief.</i>

234
00:14:28,850 --> 00:14:31,550
<i>And she kept asking me</i>

235
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:33,430
<i>holding onto me.</i>

236
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:38,260
<i>I couldn't say anything.</i>

237
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:41,540
<i>In the police car on the way to the station,</i>

238
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:44,580
<i>Cheol Woong told me he was sorry.</i>

239
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:46,760
<i>I answered him saying,</i>

240
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:48,960
<i>"What are you sorry about?"</i>

241
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:52,130
<i>"You are human, while I'm the son of a servant."</i>

242
00:14:52,130 --> 00:14:56,030
<i>"I'm pretty much a dog or a pig, so what are you sorry about?"</i>

243
00:14:56,030 --> 00:15:00,010
<i>And like that, I came here.</i>

244
00:15:00,010 --> 00:15:04,550
<i>The son of a servant dreamed a useless dream.</i>

245
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:07,040
<i>I dreamed of becoming a Korean Literature teacher,</i>

246
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:11,950
<i>and of eating dinner with Jung Shin who looks pretty with her pigtails</i>

247
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:14,860
<i>when I come home from work.</i>

248
00:15:15,860 --> 00:15:20,350
<i>That was a ridiculous ambition.</i>

249
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:23,600
<i>How dare Lee Doo Hak, the son of a servant...</i>

250
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:26,990
<i>Lee Doo Hak, who is nothing more than a dog or a pig...</i>

