00:47:52,950 --> 00:47:54,190
Jin Hee...

741
00:47:54,190 --> 00:47:56,400
- Yes?
- Well...

742
00:47:56,400 --> 00:47:58,400
check this address for me.

743
00:47:59,880 --> 00:48:02,150
- Yes.
- Thanks.

744
00:48:02,150 --> 00:48:03,390
[From: No Sook Ja*, 43-205 Dongja-dong, Yongsan-gu, Seoul-si]

