00:48:08,580 --> 00:48:09,850
This is the Seoul subway station.

746
00:48:09,850 --> 00:48:12,280
- The Seoul subway station?
- Yes.

747
00:48:15,320 --> 00:48:16,460
Yes, hello?

748
00:48:16,460 --> 00:48:18,290
Prosecutor Kim Sung Yeob...

749
00:48:18,290 --> 00:48:21,150
did you get my mail?

750
00:48:25,200 --> 00:48:27,710
Are you the homeless man in Seoul station?

751
00:48:27,710 --> 00:48:30,190
